{"tid":1452412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"郭文貴：中共派7萬便衣臥底香港","createTime":"2019-08-12T01:10:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T01:05:01.000Z","uid":184679,"like":13,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"293d41a53ebf82b76df48b94d8643542c78d61fc","tid":1452412,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:10:52.000Z","msg":"香港反送中遊行！現在警民間衝突升高，更傳出香港即將實施戒嚴，讓情勢更加緊張。流亡的中國富商郭文貴對此在直播上爆料，中共安插至少7萬名便衣進香港，將會配合香港政府對付示威群眾。<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴先前就說，香港將會實施戒嚴，他日前直播再度爆料，稱據可靠的消息指出，中共在8月4日那天派出3萬人進入香港，5日、6日又分別進入3萬人左右，不低於7萬人，且到8月12日為止，潛入香港的人數一定不會低於12萬人，持續滲入香港中。郭文貴指出，他們這些人有不同的任務，有的是駐港人員、遊客等，換了裝潛伏進香港。<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴爆料，總共發給這些人4套衣服，包括黑衫、白衫、香港警服，還有在特殊情況下穿的集體服裝，應該是紅衣裝，都是有標誌的。<br />\n<br />\n「8月4號戒嚴，一點沒錯！」郭文貴怒批，中共這種行為是「王八蛋，太王八蛋了」，香港人實在太老實善良，未來就會知道了，還會有視頻佐證。郭文貴感嘆，共產黨對香港的一系列的舉動上，能看出來共產黨能領導中國這個國家，「是人類史上最荒唐的事情。」<br />\n<br />\n香港反送中運動，示威群眾穿上黑衣，要求港府撤回有疑慮的《逃犯條例》，數以百萬的港人走上街頭，表達訴求。怎料港府不正視民眾訴求，更讓民眾與政府、警方間產生了極度的不信任感，風波越演越烈，爆發多起流血衝突。香港特首林鄭月娥對此宣布，《逃犯條例》已壽終正寢，但只要沒有撤回的一天，港人就擔心該條例恐「起死回生」，繼續抗議行動。<br />\n<br />\n然而，警民衝突繼續升溫，現在更爆出有黑社會介入，在上月21日竟有穿著白衣的大批人士，竟闖入元朗地鐵站無差別暴打市民，這一幕震驚全球。而香港政府、警方的消極作為，令港人相當失望，除了要求撤回《逃犯條例》，更要林鄭月娥下台負責，港人還發起罷工、罷課、罷市「香港三罷」行動，由航空業帶頭響應，表達對政府的不滿。<br />\n<br />\n對此，林鄭月娥本月5日召開記者會表示，少數暴力份子一連串極端暴力行為，罔顧他人權利及自由，並將香港推向極端危險的境況，包括污損國徽、將國旗拆下丟入海裡、揚言搞革命、光復香港等，認為已經讓原本的政治訴求變了調，挑戰國家主權，危害一國兩制的行為，會摧毀香港的穩定繁榮。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說道，她明白人民對政府有所不滿，但不代表可以縱容暴力，她希望市民能想一想，是否要押上700萬人的生活、及香港的未來做為賭注，她痛批「這種玉石俱焚的做法，只會將香港推向不歸路。」<br />\n<br />\n至於是否願意下台，林鄭月娥重申，個人或官員下台無法解決問題，她會帶領香港離開困境，盼盡快恢復社會秩序。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/qMPYsE.vnLaF5A5IwMG3ow--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MC4xNTY4NjI3NDUwOTgwNw--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/setn.com.tw/a844f7da8de90f8d20ad57e742a6cac2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FqMPYsE.vnLaF5A5IwMG3ow--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MC4xNTY4NjI3NDUwOTgwNw--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fsetn.com.tw%2Fa844f7da8de90f8d20ad57e742a6cac2&h=dfc615d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/郭文貴爆-中共派7萬便衣臥底香港-040030756.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E9%83%AD%E6%96%87%E8%B2%B4%E7%88%86-%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E6%B4%BE7%E8%90%AC%E4%BE%BF%E8%A1%A3%E8%87%A5%E5%BA%95%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-040030756.html&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=f8a9206b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/郭文貴爆-中共派7萬便衣臥底香港-040030756.html</a>"},{"pid":"ad98b4e47e6c9d1d96349707d68249c011afe6d0","tid":1452412,"uid":303778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:19:27.000Z","msg":"同中國割席"},{"pid":"e99794689ad55d120920788c91cfe18f6bc4e70e","tid":1452412,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb99c79330218209608cce9f9e95b1bc4bfb807","tid":1452412,"uid":38548,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:28:16.000Z","msg":"呢條撚屌收皮啦"},{"pid":"4bad8391d3182327b37bba7619b6adf8afb966f1","tid":1452412,"uid":44646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:28:33.000Z","msg":"唔好SHARE條撚樣啦<br />\n<br />\n又聲波炮，又8.5老解"},{"pid":"410a7ec45f4fec781000018e7ecab790e5dd7a22","tid":1452412,"uid":294578,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:29:05.000Z","msg":"敦文貴夠話8月5出老解啦"},{"pid":"3ef40309da10b4732e1303c98e80ebb3379fdf49","tid":1452412,"uid":38548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9cb99c79330218209608cce9f9e95b1bc4bfb807","tid":1452412,"uid":38548,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:28:16.000Z","msg":"呢條撚屌收皮啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:29:11.000Z","msg":"講D 似是而非既事實等人覺得佢講野可信<br />\n<br />\n實際上想滲透維穩意識幫中共做白面"},{"pid":"ccb96dcdd5636a459c639032dcf31f42228df979","tid":1452412,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:36:35.000Z","msg":"8月4日以後, 林奠信心十足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"befb3be8df9f5a01311b06e3c89e4e754b0a283a","tid":1452412,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:46:47.000Z","msg":"8月4日以後, 克驚加大力度克制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a137379211e664899a4e78a7f21470d53c7481","tid":1452412,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:48:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"424aab67c9632b4b34e5cb8996e42003c809b966","tid":1452412,"uid":181088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"410a7ec45f4fec781000018e7ecab790e5dd7a22","tid":1452412,"uid":294578,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:29:05.000Z","msg":"敦文貴夠話8月5出老解啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:53:40.000Z","msg":"出左啦<br />\n換左衫之ma"},{"pid":"10369b3a107cb3b86395cb4ded216a813f9545d8","tid":1452412,"uid":32719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RntuKxi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRntuKxi.jpg&h=2d720f36&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kNktfDZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkNktfDZ.jpg&h=5d6abd42&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gk0wXSn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgk0wXSn.jpg&h=b2d98c3e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dV4xHi5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdV4xHi5.jpg&h=8aeecf39&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WrKE6LM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWrKE6LM.png&h=b9706757&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DL2GAD7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDL2GAD7.png&h=2d6e2c7a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ARU9Kxu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FARU9Kxu.png&h=a32d7290&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ki2Wpxw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fki2Wpxw.jpg&h=ad0dcc4a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LEuNwcz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLEuNwcz.jpg&h=ea6c9a69&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EHnjnjf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEHnjnjf.png&h=694880f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f289159919c8addc12dce163709b37a1c3f6b1f8","tid":1452412,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:55:44.000Z","msg":"咪再貼呢個低能仔啦，好煩"},{"pid":"436f72ceda0fac93f3a1d6d354747b562b083eb8","tid":1452412,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:01:56.000Z","msg":"抺黑敵人是_ _ 的慣用手法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1011aacf10024a488e58c02d5221fe75c0eb63f1","tid":1452412,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:38:53.000Z","msg":"郭文貴認為，此舉意味著在關鍵時刻、攤牌時刻，可以穿上衣服識別敵我。他還警告，這些人進香港都被派遣不同的任務，在不同的機構，有的是駐港人員、有的是遊客，未來將配合港府對付示威者，鎖定對象逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n他還稱，未來會有視頻、會議的音頻釋放出來。他還特別提醒在香港現場採訪的《大紀元》和《蘋果日報》記者，說中共官方已經盯上他們。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，反送中運動爆發以來，「香港警察」的種種惡劣行徑已經令外界懷疑，中共祕密派遣到中共公安或武警在香港挑事。<br />\n<br />\n8月5日，法國《費加羅報》（Figaro）用了兩個版面篇幅，刊登了香港浸大教授高敬文的話透露，約2000名中共警察已經混入港警中，港警直接聽命於中聯辦，而非港首林鄭月娥。<br />\n<br />\n8月8日晚間，有網友拍到有人攜帶中共「武警8673部隊」字樣的行李箱現身港鐵，武警一直是鎮壓藏人和新疆人的主要武裝力量，具有豐富的「維穩」經驗。另有網傳視頻指，大批軍車繼續在深圳集結。外界質疑北京正在向香港祕密調派武裝力量<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/08/11/a102641972.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2019%2F08%2F11%2Fa102641972.html&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=ec62229d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/08/11/a102641972.html</a>"},{"pid":"e02f5765e653bf2f712a9c21710123d1afbacb08","tid":1452412,"uid":143435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:20:05.000Z","msg":"公安實有，人數唔知，信一半算"},{"pid":"edb7395348c3c637c1a307c9db041111ee44b96e","tid":1452412,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:09:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629e96e4a367279e975c7cc403a08faa5e4d5ad3","tid":1452412,"uid":279981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:10:33.000Z","msg":"fuck off<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5ac3a5bc3629ba97db916cd2756ccb8f254b33","tid":1452412,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a1820246309f0464c84cf6e91b3f92d8f64220","tid":1452412,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:24:48.000Z","msg":"又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0b19b88ac826d715bb4ba081d82a4d46516df1","tid":1452412,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:25:46.000Z","msg":"是旦啦"},{"pid":"21fd13bc9e09f1369ff288196b1d538651928d53","tid":1452412,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6e55f3ec6a975d6388eca8be3a4075221dd7e6","tid":1452412,"uid":178875,"like"